  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian response to socially excludedgroups in tiruvallur district affected by cyclone Vardah</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">950 HHs have emergency shelter having protection harsh weather . HH also receive hygience kits and safe drinking water to protect them from water borne diseases.Tarpauline shelter will be provided to HH for temporary shelters and persons who are affected with water borne diseases will be treated and will benefit from improved hygience and sanitation.
.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Distribution of non food items,  wash and hygience kits , emrgency shelter and tablets of chlonorination of water to 950 HH in Tiruvallur district of Tamil Nadu.  Apart from that capacity building onwash and hygience, solid waste management will also be provided to the communiy in 19 villages and 2 blocks of Tiruvallur district.</narrative>
  </description>
